{
  "name": "@t2000/engine",
  "version": "2.12.0",
  "description": "Agent engine for conversational finance — AISDKEngine (wraps Vercel AI SDK v6 `streamText`) with 37 tools (25 read, 12 write), 14-guard runner across 3 priority tiers, silent intelligence layer, streaming, canvas, BlockVision-backed pricing. Chat-first by design — every write requires user confirmation. Skills (orchestration playbooks) live in @t2000/mcp and are exposed to MCP clients as prompts.",
